# Overcast frontend — risk-accepted HIGH/CRITICAL image findings, time-boxed.
# Reviewed 2026-07-12. Revisit by 2026-10-01 (Dependabot bumps the base image).
#
# c-ares (async DNS resolver) in the nginx-unprivileged alpine base. Fix
# 1.34.8-r0 is not yet in the base image's alpine package repo, so it cannot be
# pulled by a base bump or `apk upgrade` today. Low reachability: this nginx
# only serves static assets and proxies to the in-cluster backend by Kubernetes
# service DNS (resolved by kube-dns), not via attacker-influenced c-ares queries.
CVE-2026-33630
